Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.03,0:00:05.64,720P-sgbd-27,,0,0,0,,Global persistent infrared surveillance continues to be a critical national security space mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.03,0:00:05.64,720P-shss-60,,0,0,0,,全球持久性红外监视仍然是一项重要的国家安全空间任务
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.14,0:00:10.08,720P-sgbd-27,,0,0,0,,The Cold War focus on strategic ICBM systems has expanded
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.14,0:00:10.08,720P-shss-60,,0,0,0,,冷战时期对战略洲际弹道导弹系统的关注已经扩展到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.12,0:00:13.26,720P-sgbd-27,,0,0,0,,to include short and mid-range ballistic missile threats.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.12,0:00:13.26,720P-shss-60,,0,0,0,,包括短程和中程弹道导弹威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.62,0:00:17.74,720P-sgbd-27,,0,0,0,,The defense support program maintains the legacy Cold War monitoring
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.62,0:00:17.74,720P-shss-60,,0,0,0,,国防支持计划保持了冷战时期的监测
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:20.86,720P-sgbd-27,,0,0,0,,to warn of ICBM missile launches against the US.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:20.86,720P-shss-60,,0,0,0,,以警告针对美国的洲际弹道导弹发射
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.23,0:00:25.32,720P-sgbd-27,,0,0,0,,The replacement programs, the Space-Based InfRared System or SBIRS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.23,0:00:25.32,720P-shss-60,,0,0,0,,替代计划 即天基红外系统或SBIRS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.36,0:00:30.76,720P-sgbd-27,,0,0,0,,which is already provided to infrared sensor payloads in Highly Elliptical Orbits or HEO.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.36,0:00:30.76,720P-shss-60,,0,0,0,,已经提供给高椭圆轨道或HEO上的红外传感器有效载荷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:37.20,720P-sgbd-27,,0,0,0,,The SBIRS program is also deploying multiple spacecraft into Geosynchronous Earth Orbit or GEO.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:37.20,720P-shss-60,,0,0,0,,SBIRS计划也正在将多个航天器部署到地球同步轨道或GEO
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.83,0:00:40.48,720P-sgbd-27,,0,0,0,,Each has two independent infrared sensors.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.83,0:00:40.48,720P-shss-60,,0,0,0,,每个都有两个独立的红外传感器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:44.92,720P-sgbd-27,,0,0,0,,One is a scanner dedicated to missile warning with full earth monitoring.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:44.92,720P-shss-60,,0,0,0,,一个是专门用于导弹预警的扫描仪 对地球进行全面监测
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.26,0:00:49.44,720P-sgbd-27,,0,0,0,,The other sensor is a taskable starer that can focus on selected regions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.26,0:00:49.44,720P-shss-60,,0,0,0,,另一个传感器是一个可执行任务的跟踪器 可以聚焦于选定的区域
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.93,0:00:54.25,720P-sgbd-27,,0,0,0,,Each pair of sensors act simultaneously and independently of each other
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.93,0:00:54.25,720P-shss-60,,0,0,0,,每对传感器同时独立工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.31,0:00:57.36,720P-sgbd-27,,0,0,0,,providing a robust castable infrared platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.31,0:00:57.36,720P-shss-60,,0,0,0,,提供了一个强大的可投射的红外平台
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.66,0:01:02.75,720P-sgbd-27,,0,0,0,,SBIRS is the nation's next generation of space-based infrared surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.66,0:01:02.75,720P-shss-60,,0,0,0,,SBIRS是国家的下一代天基红外监视
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.19,0:01:07.79,720P-sgbd-27,,0,0,0,,The program has already proven its value with successful HEO payloads on orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.19,0:01:07.79,720P-shss-60,,0,0,0,,该计划已经用成功的HEO有效载荷在轨道上证明了其价值
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.05,0:01:12.74,720P-sgbd-27,,0,0,0,,With deployment of the GEO spacecraft, SBIRS will be an unprecedented resource
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.05,0:01:12.74,720P-shss-60,,0,0,0,,随着地球同步轨道航天器的部署 SBIRS将成为一种前所未有的资源
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.87,0:01:17.85,720P-sgbd-27,,0,0,0,,as the nation's global taskable and persistent infrared monitoring sentinel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.87,0:01:17.85,720P-shss-60,,0,0,0,,作为国家的全球可执行任务和持久的红外监测哨兵 将成为一种前所未有的资源
